div.p:
                    Calls upon the Governments concerned: 
                        (i)

To order an immediate cease-fire;
                        (ii)

To implement without further delay resolution 61 (1948) of 4 November
                            1948 and the instructions issued by the Acting Mediator in accordance
                            with sub-paragraph (1) of the fifth paragraph of that resolution;
                        (iii)

To allow and facilitate the complete supervision of the truce by the
                            United Nations observers;
